</li></ul>
<a name="Alternative_Approaches"></a><h2> <span class="mw-headline"> Alternative Approaches </span></h2>
<p>Non-web based:
</p>
<ul><li> <a href="http://about.psyc.eu" class="external text" title="http://about.psyc.eu" rel="nofollow">psyc</a> and <a href="http://www.psyced.org" class="external text" title="http://www.psyced.org" rel="nofollow">psyced</a>, a decentralized multi-protocol chat and event notification system with <a href="http://about.psyc.eu/Social_Network" class="external text" title="http://about.psyc.eu/Social_Network" rel="nofollow">friendship</a> and <a href="http://about.psyc.eu/Trust" class="external text" title="http://about.psyc.eu/Trust" rel="nofollow">trust</a> modeling.
</li></ul>
